challenge.description: A crime has taken place and the detective needs your help. The detective gave you the crime scene report, but you somehow lost it. You vaguely remember that the crime was a robbery that occurred sometime on ​May 25, 2021​ and that it took place in Sioux Falls City. Start by retrieving the corresponding crime scene report from the police department’s database.

crime_scene_report.report: Security footage shows that there were 2 witnesses. The first witness lives at the last house on Hayden Key. The other named Chasity Gleason, lives somewhere on Ward Crest.

dialogs.transcript: I saw the robbery happen, and I recognized the robber from gym when I was working out on May 5, 2021.

I heard a person screaming loudly and then saw a man run out. He had a gym bag. The membership number on the bag ends with `ZTH`. Only platinum members have those bags. The man got into a car with a plate that included `BC4`.

I was hired by a man with lots of money. I don't know his name but I know he's around 167 or 178. He has blonde hair, has amber eyes and she drives a Volvo Model T. I know that he attended the The Sexy Blues Experience 3 times in 2020.
